data.title: The Collected Works of John Stuart Mill, Volume XXVII - Journals and Debating Speeches Part II
data.meta_description: Vol. 27 of the 33 vol. Collected Works contains Mill’s diaries of his walking tours 1827-32, a diary from 1854 and other material from the early 1820s.
